<Base title="About" description="About John Paul Lumpp of WriteNow.Media — writer, researcher, and publisher with more than 30 years of experience.">
  <div class="hero" style="padding-bottom:2rem;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>The person behind <span class="marked">the byline</span>.</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section style="padding-top:1rem;">
    <div class="wrap about-grid">
      <div class="prose">
      <p>
        WriteNow.Media is the practice of John Paul Lumpp — writer, researcher,
        and publisher. Across more than 30 years, the work has spanned a wide
        range of businesses — aviation, construction, entertainment, and retail
        among them — along with numerous trade publications. Through all of it,
        one conviction has held: good writing is a research problem before it
        is a language problem.
      </p>
      <p>
        Clients come here for three reasons. Businesses need someone who can
        read a spec sheet and interview an engineer, then explain the product
        in plain English. Families need someone who can read a census schedule,
        a ship manifest, and a parish register, then turn names into people.
        And authors need a collaborator who has been through the publishing
        process and knows where the manuscripts go to die.
      </p>
      <p>
        The proof of that approach is <strong>Gunns in America</strong> — fifteen
        years of research into one family line across 400 years of American
        history. The project has produced a research website at
        <a href="https://gunnsinamerica.org" rel="noopener">gunnsinamerica.org</a>,
        an ongoing newsletter at
        <a href="https://gunnsinamerica.substack.com" rel="noopener">gunnsinamerica.substack.com</a>,
        and a book — <em>The Gunns in America</em> — now in editorial review.
        It is the full arc of the work in one project: records found, lines
        traced, and a family's story written down.
      </p>
      <h2>Background</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>More than 30 years of professional writing and research</li>
        <li>Business and trade writing for aviation, construction, entertainment, and retail</li>
        <li>Contributor to numerous trade publications</li>
        <li>Author of <em>The Gunns in America</em> (forthcoming) — the culmination of 15 years of research</li>
        <li>Creator of the Gunns in America research project — website and newsletter</li>
        <li>Independent publisher — book, web, and newsletter</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="btn" href="/contact/">Work together</a></p>
      </div>
      <figure class="portrait">
        <img src="/images/jpl-portrait.jpg" alt="Engraved portrait of John Paul Lumpp" width="720" height="899" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="eyebrow">J.P. LUMPP · WRITER · RESEARCHER · PUBLISHER</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
